      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DEEP STATE (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (27.95) at this track behind Flash Of Genius in a Grade 4/5. Chased the leaders and with a clean run can be prominent. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Capable of going well again. PAW WAVERLY (5) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing seventh (28.38) last time in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Form here sound including two wins. Likely to play a prominent role. FEIKUAI CALVIN (3) had been racing in honest fashion recording two placings in a row before finishing fifth (30.84) at The Meadows latest. Has a good record at this journey. Should be about the mark. KRAKEN TOMMY (2) hit the frame latest (28.44) when second at this track in a Grade 5. Yet to taste defeat in two runs from this draw.",
